nodes.text: In 14 BBY following a mission to Bogano, the Mantis crew undertook a mission to the planet Zeffo as part of a larger secret mission to rebuild the Jedi Order.

After visiting the planet Bogano, the Mantis crew gained a new member, the BD unit droid BD-1. While at Bogano, Jedi Master Eno Cordova gave Jedi Padawan Cal Kestis a task, telling him to go the the Zeffo homeworld, Zeffo.
